            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for efficiently synthesizing formamide by catalyzing lower amine and carbon dioxide through a polymer-based catalyst, which comprises the following steps: by taking the lower amine or ammonium salt generated by the lower amine and carbon dioxide as an amine source, reacting at 80-160 DEG C for 4-48 hours in the presence of carbon dioxide and hydrogen under the action of the polymer-based catalyst to synthesize the formamide. Formamide is catalytically synthesized by adopting the polymer-based catalyst, no additional alkali is needed, and the synthesis method is simple, low in cost and high in efficiency; the polymer-based catalyst is not used in a reaction system, is easy to separate and is very convenient to recycle."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种聚合物基催化剂催化低级胺与二氧化碳高效合成甲酰胺的方法，是以低级胺或低级胺与二氧化碳生成的铵盐为胺源，在二氧化碳和氢气参与条件下，聚合物基催化剂的作用下，于80~160℃下反应4~48h，合成甲酰胺。本发明制备采用聚合物基催化剂催化合成甲酰胺，不需要外加碱的参与，合成方法简单，成本低，效率高；聚合物基催化剂不用于反应体系，容易分离，回收利用十分方便。"
                }
            ]
